response.overview: However, all of the job search techniques that we perfected during that period have not fallen to the wayside. Over the past couple of years, we've been able to assist a number of people with their job search, developing effective resumes and cover letters, and availing them of a variety of services and job banks that we came across while looking for work. Carrying out a job search is not always easy, however, with persistence and resourcefulness, your efforts will pay off in time.
response.title: Carrying out
